page.title: 20Beetham Survey Group
page.content: The Third and Fourth Years of Storth Primary School enjoyed surveying the Beetham area. The Fourth Years were; Nicholas Linton, Ian Wood, Kieran Stewart, Robert Black, Lisa Phipps, Alison Thompson, Elizabeth Pearson, Rebecca Eastham, Judith Farrell. The Third Years were;Nathan Heyes, Nigel Carey, Daniel Clowes, Ian Howell, Sarah Duckworth, Yvonne Seed, Katie Wilson, Philippa Horner, Jane Wilkinson. Some First Years helped to type. They were Kirsty Parry, Victoria Eastham and Lucy Ree. We are very grateful to the parents who helped to ferry us around.
